message.body: Mom never gets a callback from your roommate. Do you know why? We thought he was really excited to get started.
Nope. Im trying to stay out of that stuff but ill ask him. Hes not here and wont be back until next week
Ok. I'm always suspicious about this stuff, but I'm at another meeting with mom tonight and it really seems like a no brainer. Get residual income on people's
energy bills. You don't have sell things. It just keeps going.
U have to get people to change energy companies. And is ignite definitely cheaper?
Right. And no, but it often is. It's not more so they switch because they're your friend.
Yeah. Ed seemed excited to me at first but i dunno what hes done if anything. Havent really talked to him about it
Do you want to come to our gig on March 29 at Cutillo's in Pottstown?
No i cant ill be in the hospital for a study that night
